scripts.name: Address: add link to directions from church
scripts.description: Add a new link under the profile's address to directions from the profile's campus to them, to make it easier to see how far they are.

scripts.name: Fix Advanced Search button hitbox
scripts.description: Fix a bug where the button to go to Advanced Search doesn't register if you don't click right in the middle.

scripts.name: Fix cursor not turning to pointer on some buttons/links
scripts.description: Like the ones on the sidebar.

scripts.name: Groups: Fix CSV Export "Take Action On" setting
scripts.description: Fix a bug that causes F1 to ignore your "Take action on" setting in the CSV Export in this page. I.e., you can export parents from this page now.

scripts.name: Interaction Reminder Template
scripts.description: Add a little table row to the side of the screen that you can copy and paste straight into Outstanding Interactions emails.

scripts.name: Submit on Enter
scripts.description: Go when you press Enter.

scripts.name: Move the Delete button to the left
scripts.description: Move the Edit Profile delete button farther away from the save button to make it harder to click on accident.

scripts.name: Type / to search
scripts.description: Keyboard shortcut inspired by GitHub. Press / to focus the search bar.

scripts.name: White Logo
scripts.description: Change the James River logo from black to white. This is the color it usually is when we put it on blue.

scripts.name: Dark Reader checkbox fix
scripts.description: (For Dark Reader): restore a visual distinction between checkboxes and are and are not grayed out.

scripts.name: Fix group X button hitbox
scripts.description: Expand the tiny hitbox of the delete button on groups.

scripts.name: Fix sidebar item hitboxes
scripts.description: The left and right edges of the buttons don't register.

scripts.name: Relationship to JRC Date: add Today button
scripts.description: Add a button to the Relationship to JRC Date field that sets it to today's date.

scripts.name: Make profiles in Search Bar behave like real links
scripts.description: So that you can right click them, copy their links, open them in a new tab, etc.

scripts.name: Edit: Fix home phone and cell phone tab order
scripts.description: Put their tab indexes in the order that they are on the screen.

scripts.name: Schedules: Link people to profiles
scripts.description: Make people's names on schedules links that you can click in order to see their profiles.

scripts.name: Edit/Add: Increase Groups list height to fit four groups
scripts.description: I want to be able to see four groups, because that is the usual number I add to new profiles.

scripts.name: Saved place note: Ctrl+Enter to submit

scripts.name: Fill in profile pictures in the Family Section
scripts.description: None

scripts.name: My Interactions notification bubble
scripts.description: Add a notification bubble to the navbar for outstanding Interactions assigned to you.

scripts.name: Export all if none selected
scripts.description: If I don't have anyone selected, I want to export everyone.

scripts.name: GT Info + Clickable Search Profiles
scripts.description: Adds Grade/DOB/Gender info to top search dropdown and makes names clickable links

scripts.name: Assign Interaction: warn for calls/texts if number not present
scripts.description: Warn if you try to assign certain interactions on a profile that doesn't have a phone number.

scripts.description: Warn if you try to assign New Visitor Cookie Visit interaction on a profile that doesn't have an address.

scripts.name: View Individual: View image attachments in page
scripts.description: If an attachment on a profile is an image, add a viewer to it so you don't have to download it.

scripts.name: Attendance: autoswitch
scripts.description: Switch between attendance sessions without asking.

scripts.name: Hide section collapse buttons
scripts.description: Hide the buttons that let you minimize sections in the Add/Edit page. I've never clicked them on purpose but I have clicked them on accident.

scripts.name: Taller Assign Interaction popup
scripts.description: So the whole thing fits on screen at once.

scripts.name: Family Assign Interaction: fix action dropdown width
scripts.description: Fix some messed up CSS in the Assign Interaction popup on the Family page.

scripts.name: Add/Edit: add Last Service button to some dates
scripts.description: Add a button that sets its to the closest past Sunday or Wednesday, in the fields that are usually set to last service.

scripts.name: Family page: Fix Assign To comment font
scripts.description: Fix an odd wrong font setting for this little piece of text on just this page.

scripts.name: Attendance Reports: Fix "Last 6 Months"
scripts.description: Fix the date range to actually be the last six months when the "Last 6 Months" setting is chosen.

scripts.name: Assign Interactions add Formal Full Name

scripts.name: Add Individuals to Group show contact info
scripts.description: Adds Formal Full Name Assign Interactions search dropdown

scripts.description: Integrate USPS address validation and autofill into the Address fields.

scripts.description: Integrate USPS address validation into the Address field.

scripts.description: What's the first thing you do on the Interactions page? Open the filter box! So why not have it open by itself?

scripts.name: Edit Individual - Groups: focus input in Add tab

scripts.name: Assign Interaction: Ctrl+Enter to submit
scripts.description: Add Ctrl+Enter as a hotkey for clicking Save on Assign Interaction.

scripts.name: Assign Interaction: autofill due date

scripts.name: View: add check for missing family
